            <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">After filling (6) six showcase spots the contestants will be voted on by the viewing or listening internet participant (judges) first to narrow the members down to [3] three and then to [1] one member who earns the spotlight. That member will be given the opportunity to sell their  video to UnseenTalents.com for $500.00 United States Dollars which will be paid out using the PayPal service .</p>
