            <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Now voting for the top [6] six will begin and after [1] one week of voting the top [3] three will be revealed.</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Now voting for the top [3] will begin and after [1] one week of voting the top [1] one or showcase will be revealed .</p>
