            <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">This cycle will be repeated until there are [6] six members in a showcase .</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">At that point the voting will begin for that level of the competition .</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Voting for the [6] six showcase members will go for [1] one week  and the  top [3] three of the showcase will be revealed .</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Next voting for the top [3] will run for [1] one week and then the top spot or SPOTLIGHT  member will be crowned and receive an offer to sell their  video  via the PayPal service .</p>
